title: Food and beverage / palm oil
content: These gas turbines from our portfolio are best suited for food and beverage / sugar and ethanol / palm oil applications and have a track record of successful reference cases. In addition, we offer more gas turbine models in a wide power output range, which may fit your individual needs.
